source: TEXT_STMBDZ222_02694_SEQ_00<tab>Toro is in need of a pair of strong arms.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ222_02694_SEQ_00<tab>碧のタマミズのトウロウは、力自慢の旅人を探しているようだ。

source: TEXT_STMBDZ222_02694_TORO_000_000<tab>Would you take a look at those brawny arms! You appear to be as strong as me─if not stronger! I would bet all my treasure that you, too, could kill a flying shark with your bare hands.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ222_02694_TORO_000_000<tab>オメーさん、力自慢かぁ～？
オイラもちっとばかし、腕っ節には自信があるんだぁ～。
トビザメだって、締め上げてみせるさぁ～！

source: TEXT_STMBDZ222_02694_TORO_000_001<tab>The other day I purchased this stone of vitality from a merchant on the surface. He promised me that wearing it would grant me immense physical might.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ222_02694_TORO_000_001<tab>とはいえ、それだけじゃ不安でなぁ～。
この<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8D5901 /var>をヒトの商人から買ったんだぁ～。
なんでも、持ってるだけで力が沸いてくる、すごいお宝よぉ～。

source: TEXT_STMBDZ222_02694_TORO_000_002<tab>I have gone out and tested it against all manner of wild beast but it did not seem to have any effect. Could you give it a try? I suspect there is a trick to making it work that I have not yet figured out myself.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ222_02694_TORO_000_002<tab>だがなぁ、どうにも効果が実感できねえんだぁ～。
こいつを貸すから、ちょっくら試してきてくれないかぁ～？

source: TEXT_STMBDZ222_02694_TORO_000_003<tab>Mayhap you can test it out against some of the unkiu to the east of here. These beasts are said to have shells as hard as diamond and are nigh indestructible.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ222_02694_TORO_000_003<tab>そうさなぁ、「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F2166701 /var>」の甲羅なら、いい塩梅に固いなぁ～。
この石をもって、何匹か倒したら、効果を教えてほしいんだぁ～。
やつら、この里の入口あたりの入り江にいるから、頼んだぞぉ～。

source: TEXT_STMBDZ222_02694_TORO_000_004<tab>Please, take the stone of vitality and test it out on the unkiu to the east of here.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ222_02694_TORO_000_004<tab><var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8D5901 /var>を持って、
この里の入口あたりにいる「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F2166701 /var>」を、倒してきてくれぇ～。
そんで効果があったら、教えてほしいんだぁ～。

source: TEXT_STMBDZ222_02694_TORO_100_010<tab>So, tell me, adventurer─did the stone of vitality work?
target: TEXT_STMBDZ222_02694_TORO_100_010<tab><var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8D5901 /var>の効果は、どうだったぁ～？

source: TEXT_STMBDZ222_02694_TORO_000_010<tab>You could not tell if it had any effect? <sigh> The merchant did warn me that the stone would do little for those who have already attained true power.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ222_02694_TORO_000_010<tab>やっぱり、わかんなかったかぁ～。
だが、売ってくれたヒトも言ってたなぁ～。
本当の強さを手に入れたとき、<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8D5901 /var>はいらなくなるってよぉ～。

source: TEXT_STMBDZ222_02694_TORO_000_011<tab>Mayhap the both of us are simply too strong to receive any of its benefits.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ222_02694_TORO_000_011<tab>きっとオイラはもう、強くなりすぎちまったんだなぁ～。
オメーさんも強そうだし、きっとそうだぁ～。

source: TEXT_STMBDZ222_02694_TORO_000_012<tab>While the thing may have cost me a fortune, I do not regret a single koban I spent on it. This rock has proven to me that I have what it takes to protect my people and my village, and that I need nothing more than my two arms and legs to do it.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ222_02694_TORO_000_012<tab>オイラはこの腕っ節で、里のみんなと、お宝を護っていくよぉ～。
傷つけるためじゃねえ、傷つけさせないためになぁ～。

source: TEXT_STMBDZ222_02694_TORO_000_013<tab>I shall be keeping the stone of vitality as a reminder of that. Thank you for all your help. You have allowed me to come to a very important realization today.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ222_02694_TORO_000_013<tab>そんじゃあ、礼と<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8D5901 /var>を交換しよう～。
この石は、オイラの決意の記念に大事にするよぉ～。
ありがとな、力自慢のヒトよぉ～。
